  "detailed_description": "You're in the role of a former professional baseball player in a post-apocalyptic city. You can only count on your good old bat to deal with the imminent infestation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703130/extras/6116539720fa4f61005dfb99e55596f7.poster.avif?t=1751385525\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703130/extras/6116539720fa4f61005dfb99e55596f7.webm?t=1751385525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703130/extras/6116539720fa4f61005dfb99e55596f7.mp4?t=1751385525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A small open world for you to explore.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Countless character skins for you to choose from.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Countless enemies with fun visuals.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Highscore system for you to challenge yourself.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Immersive day and night weather system.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fun and memorable sound effects.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Responsive controls.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Advanced settings for better player experience.</li></ul><br>And more secrets to discover!",
  "about_the_game": "You're in the role of a former professional baseball player in a post-apocalyptic city. You can only count on your good old bat to deal with the imminent infestation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703130/extras/6116539720fa4f61005dfb99e55596f7.poster.avif?t=1751385525\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703130/extras/6116539720fa4f61005dfb99e55596f7.webm?t=1751385525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703130/extras/6116539720fa4f61005dfb99e55596f7.mp4?t=1751385525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A small open world for you to explore.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Countless character skins for you to choose from.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Countless enemies with fun visuals.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Highscore system for you to challenge yourself.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Immersive day and night weather system.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fun and memorable sound effects.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Responsive controls.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Advanced settings for better player experience.</li></ul><br>And more secrets to discover!",
